Usage: reportRC [-help] <<fileName>> [-inst <string>] -layer <string>
                [-max_second_rc <float>]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
<<fileName>>               # Specifies report file name (string, required)
-inst <string>             # Specifies the inst to report (string, optional)
-layer <string>            # Specify the layer of obs to calculate
                           # (string, required)
-max_second_rc <float>     # Specify the max distance to calculate second RC,
                           # default is 2 (float, optional)